name: Jabba's Influence (V)
Lore: 'Jabba makes offers one cannot refuse. Smugglers, thieves and competitors who do not acquiesce have been rumored to wake up with a bantha''s head in their bed.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Your gangsters are information brokers. Your bounty hunters (except Boba Fett) are power +1. While Xizor on table, Scum And Villainy ignores Emperor. Once per game, if Jabba at Audience Chamber, may deploy a non-bounty hunter alien on table from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
